casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Woodson, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Woodson (1999), 84 Ohio St.3d 309.]

(No. 98-1668 Submitted November 10, 1998 Decided January 13, 1999.) *310Michael A. Bednar, Cuyahoga County Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellant.

The judgment of the court of appeals is reversed on the authority of State v. Rush (1998), 83 Ohio St.3d 53, 697 N.E.2d 634.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
